Package: CiteDrive
Type: Package
Title: CiteDrive 'BibTeX' Companion for R Markdown
Version: 1.0.0
Author: CiteDrive LLC
Maintainer: Nadja Stieger <nadja.stieger@stud.hn.de>
Description: The CiteDrive addin sources informetric metadata from Crossref (www.crossref.org) und Semantic Scholar
    (www.semanticscholar.org) and processes it for output or further usage with other R-functions.
